---

<Layout>
	<main class="w-3/4 md:w-1/2 flex flex-wrap relative justify-center mix-blend-exclusion
">
		<h1 class="uppercase font-sans text-[6vw] md:text-[4vw] font-bold text-black">Bruce Moerdjiman</h1>
		<h2 class="text-normal text-center text-[2vw] md:text-[1.4vw] tracking-[0.3em] w-full bg-black text-white py-2">🏄🏻‍♂️ currently offline 🏄🏻‍♂️</h2>

		<p class="text-center w-full text-normal text-monospace font-light text-[1.6vw] md:text-[1.2vw] tracking-[0.2em] pt-[2vw] text-black">
			..::~ crafting digital stuff since 2000 ~::..
		</p>
	</main>

</Layout>
<Background/>
<style>
	h2{
		font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
	}

</style>
